At Bosch, we contribute to shaping the future by using high-quality technologies in manufacturing, in a way that sparks enthusiasm and enrich people’s lives. Our promise to our associates is rock-solid: we grow together, we enjoy our work, and we inspire each other. Join in and feel the difference!Bosch is producing in Blaj for more than fourteen years, first in the industrial technology sector, then in the automotive field too.In Blaj, we are a competitive plant, focused on quality of the products from all areas: linear motion technology, industrial hydraulic or the wide range of car sensors and transmission control components we are manufacturing here. The unit has developed at an accelerated pace over the years, both in terms of buildings and product portfolio. The Bosch plant in Blaj is one of three Bosch plants in Europe where emission sensors are produced, an essential component of the company's revolutionary innovation in diesel technology, and one of the few Bosch locations on the continent where electronic modules for the automatic transmission are manufactured. In addition, we have a 20 000 sm Bosch logistic center right on our production site./n

