Hard skills

	Completed studies in Computer Science/ Business Informatics or comparable qualification
	Language skills needed: English-Mandatory & German- is an advantage;
	Advanced understanding of IT technology, architectures, processes and digital trend
	Ability to focus on business value results and not just the solutions;
	Ability to identify risks & dependencies in advance and apply appropriate risk management strategies / risk management and audits;
	Knowledge of IT Infrastructure services management and associated Processes / Primary tactical contact for IT infrastructure topics;
	Ability to collaborate with highly skilled Architects and IT professionals;
	Experience working with multiple internal/ external service providers in offshore countries/ supplier management of contracts/ OLA/ SLA/ invoicing.


Soft skills


	Drive of innovation / strategic, creative and innovative thinking;
	Execution excellence;
	Relationship-building with various business and IT stakeholders;
	Negotiating and problem-solving skills / good conflict management skills;
	Collaborative and to encourage collaboration;
	High analytical/ strategic/ conceptual competence Team, communication and integration skills;
	Intercultural competence.

The IT Solution Architect is responsible for the design and development of end-to-end IT Cloud Infrastructures and IT Software Architectures for functional and non-functional requirements. He is advising Business Partners on the basis of Enterprise and Service Architecture standards. The aim is to provide a End-to-End working IT infrastructure for the digital tool together with a DevOps team or other partners. Your input comes from a Business & Application Analyst in cooperation with Technical Product Owner.
He is the primary IT contact of his area for the business partner for all relevant topics such as consulting, requirements management, service provision and operation, so that business-oriented IT solutions can be provided in cooperation with the architects and specialists.

Main responsibilities

	Defining and setting up the perfect IT cloud infrastructure and software architecture for the digital tool or product;
	Supporting and consulting business partners in setting up the software architecture and cloud infrastructure;
	Understanding business and stakeholders’ requirements and transforming them into technical solutions;
	Defining overall technical and development guidelines for products, or integrating them over several products within a clusters;
	Selecting suitable service and process models, as well as conceptual design, of the architecture according Business Analyst's requirements;
	Provides technical guidance, feedback and assistance with debugging complex problems.
The Sebes and Cugir manufacturing locations in Romania, which include the Star Transmission headquarters in Cugir and Star Assembly location in Sebes, are Mercedes-Benz AG wholly owned subsidiaries and are an important part of the Mercedes-Benz Cars global powertrain production network.The Sebeş location assembles transmissions for Mercedes-Benz.The Cugir plant is home to the production of gears, shafts, high-pressure pipes and mechanically processed components for engines, transmissions and steering systems, as well as a technology center with i.a. prototype production.With support from the Romanian government, Star Transmission is one of the first Romanian companies to offer a dual education system based on the German model in Baden-Württemberg. As partners of the program, Star Transmission and Star Assembly offer practical training in their respected establishments./n

